comment: This is a page from a classical Chinese dictionary or lexicographical text, likely a version of the *Shuowen Jiezi* or similar work. Each entry provides the character, its meaning, phonetic information (via '切' — cutting/phonetic notation), and etymological structure ('从山...' — composed of mountain radical plus other components).
